Atmos - Different spheres or dimensions. The origin of certain kin, monsters, and magic

Heaven and Hell are both spheres, neither on of them is the habitat of the authority or the adversary
Heaven and Hell are both reachable by aither a large ladder or a deep tunnel.
The BIG church is a holy city, think Vatican, at the center of which is a large tower that looks to be broken. Legen has it that it once reached into the heavens.
The heavens are right above the vatican and a visible dark cloud constantly swirls above the tower though q bright golden light is constantly movving and breaking through the cloud 
